#### § 40.375 How does the initiating official start a PIE proceeding?

(a) As a service agent, if your compliance matter is not correctable (see [§ 40.373(a)](/current/title-49/section-40.373#p-40.373\(a\))), or if have not resolved compliance matters as provided in [§ 40.373(c)](/current/title-49/section-40.373#p-40.373\(c\)), the initiating official starts a PIE proceeding by sending you a notice of proposed exclusion (NOPE). The NOPE contains the initiating official's recommendations concerning the issuance of a PIE, but it is not a decision by the Department to issue a PIE.

